Package: dir2json
Type: Package
Title: Shiny Application for an Interactive Tree View of a Folder or Hierarchical Data 
Version: 3.0.0
Date: 2022-02-25
Author: Stéphane Laurent
Maintainer: Stéphane Laurent <laurent_step@outlook.fr>
Description: Hierarchical structure of a folder as a JSON string, and a Shiny application to represent hierarchical data (such as the content of a folder) as an interactive D3 tree.
    Also returns the tree view of a folder.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, testthat, tibble
VignetteBuilder: knitr, magrittr, V8, networkD3, jsonlite
Imports: shiny, rChoiceDialogs, stringi, readxl
NeedsCompilation: no
